Ebru was also known as Dilan Pirinc. She had received death threats before being stabbed to death in her apartment.

> Ebru had asked the Prosecutor's Office for protection from the man who had beaten her on several occasions and threatened to kill her. Lambda Istanbul was told that a few weeks ago police detained the man but released him two hours later. The same man is under police custody as the murder suspect."  -Press Release from Human Rights Watch,   March 13, 2009

Virgen was a sex worker. She was shot multiple times between 19th and 21st March.

Police suspect that she was murdered by a client when he realised that she was trans. Afterwards he threw her body into the river.

El Sol de Sinaloa 24.03.2009

Her head and sexual organs had been cut off.
